OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fshowery outbreaks of rain. Turning
OL,7,Fbrighter through the afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome sunnier spells developing and
OL,9,Fshowers becoming fewer later. Breezy,
OL,10,Fespecially around coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLate sunny spells as showers
OL,13,Fclear away this evening. The rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will see mostly dry
OL,15,Fconditions, perhaps the odd light
OL,16,Fshower in the west. Patchy rural frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FFairly cloudy but dry for most
OL,19,Fplaces. The best of the sunnier spells
OL,20,Fare expected early in the morning and
OL,21,Flate in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
